{"tid":1841851,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"現眼報？新鴻基帝逸酒店確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-25T12:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T12:01:01.000Z","uid":68779,"like":303,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9f30320979cef6d1122a92ec566c9eeffcf409","tid":1841851,"uid":68779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"病人與太太居於馬鞍山天宇海，太太及父母均沒有出現病徵。病人曾於<span style=\"color: red;\">1月20日入住沙田石門帝逸酒店</span>。資料顯示，帝逸酒店去年12月才開業，<span style=\"color: red;\">屬新地旗下</span>。<br />\n<br />\n20號入住，單新聞到23號先出街，20, 21, 22 足足三日時間。肯定成間酒店既冷氣系統都唔使要了，全部換過哂等同拆左成間酒店起過間新既一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=78DDwFAlsxY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D78DDwFAlsxY&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=b1bd0c48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=78DDwFAlsxY</a><br />\nAlfred 仲要15號出左片，出完片一定多左人去食。Alfred仲要話間野好似酒樓咁放架廚餘車係客人隔離，隨時食到人地口水. 假如果家人食足酒店早餐，午餐，lounge下午茶，夜間Alfred間自助餐，再去做gym遊水做spa，真係做到全方位送大禮比SHK<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca3120324cdaf73a8e8d1e5f34804459285e42a","tid":1841851,"uid":54946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"皇"},{"pid":"8782b359bd4fe1c6c13108d63520792d93375252","tid":1841851,"uid":25601,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"所有感染左既人可以入去隔離啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360a61453350082f211f05a3944fdc1ff6b850d5","tid":1841851,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:06:35.000Z","msg":"嘩，通風槽大劑"},{"pid":"e2d6269012ef37d20e86d0b4bfb4287866cc3b70","tid":1841851,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T12:07:18.000Z","msg":"Dklm"},{"pid